NonCommercial means not primarily intended for or directed toward commercial advantage or monetary compensation.

Share means to provide material to the public.

Sui Generis Database Rights means rights other than copyright resulting from Directive 96/9/EC or equivalent.

You means the individual or entity exercising rights under this Public License.

